        "title": "Edge Class Library",
        "subtitle": "Canonical library for reusable edge-class artifacts. Plain edges remain valid without classes; this library exists for relationship semantics that need to be taught, reused, previewed, and shared, including outbound graph navigation and local in-graph content.",
